                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of magnetic phase change composite material, assembly for photo-thermal energy storage magnetic switch and energy storage method",
                    "一种磁性相变复合材料的制备方法、光热储能磁开关用组件及储能方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a preparation method of a magnetic phase change composite material, an assembly for a photo-thermal energy storage magnetic switch and an energy storage method, and belongs to the technical field of energy storage. The method comprises the following steps: firstly, preparing a uniformly mixed paraffin/Fe3O4 mixed solution by adopting an ultrasonic method, and then adding an SEBS elastomer into the mixed solution under ultrasonic treatment to obtain the magnetic phase change composite material. According to the photo-thermal energy storage method, the magnetic phase change composite material which is good in photo-thermal conversion effect and high in repeated utilization rate is adopted, the energy storage process can be rapidly completed, the heat storage amount is large, the added paraffin and Fe3O4 do not affect the heat storage process, the shape is stable in the heat storage process, meanwhile, heat storage and heat preservation can be conducted by adjusting the permanent magnet, and the energy storage effect is good. The adopted raw materials are widely used in the market, the cost is low, and the economic benefits and environmental benefits of photo-thermal energy storage are improved. A solar device is adopted in the whole hydrogen production process, a power source can be combined with other new energy processes such as wind power and photoelectricity, and fossil energy consumption and carbon emission are reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种磁性相变复合材料的制备方法、光热储能磁开关用组件及储能方法，属于储能技术领域。所述方法为：首先采用超声法制备混合均匀的石蜡/Fe3O4混合溶液，然后将SEBS弹性体在超声处理下加入上述混合溶液，得到磁性相变复合材料。本发明光热储能的方法，采用光热转换效果较好、重复利用率高的磁性相变复合材料，可以快速完成储能过程，且储热量大，添加的石蜡以及Fe3O4不影响储热过程，储热过程形状稳定的同时，还能通过调整永磁体进行储热以及保温，采用的原料皆是市场广泛使用的，成本低，提高了光热储能的经济效益和环境效益。并且整个制氢过程采用太阳能装置，电源可以与其他新能源过程结合，比如风电和光电等，降低化石能源消耗和碳排放。"
                }
            ]
